Package: proxkube
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Proxmox LXC orchestrator with Kubernetes-like pod semantics
 proxkube orchestrates Proxmox VE LXC containers using a Kubernetes-like
 pod abstraction. It supports OCI images, Docker Compose, Helm charts,
 Kubernetes operators, and includes a Proxmox dashboard plugin.
 .
 Features include a monitoring daemon that watches Proxmox configuration
 changes and manages Prometheus-based monitoring via the Kubernetes
 Prometheus operator.
